                                                                                                                                    Good Morning

   Hello It's Sunday, January 13, 2008
       
	Roads to avoid
  AJC Bose Road, Hospital Road, Queensway, Cathedral Road, Casuarina Avenue, Lovers Lane, Rani Rashmoni Avenue, JL Nehru Road, Lenin Sarani, SN Banerjee Road, APC Road, Gas Street and Raja Dinendra Street from 8am to 6pm for the Brigade Rally by CPM.
    
	Travel amp; culture 
  Dont miss Chhau dance and a performance by Bombay Vikings at West Bengal Tourism and Food Festival, organised in association with The Telegraph, at Nalban, noon to 8pm.				 																																	
 Check out Carpe Diem, a cultural fest, in association with The Telegraph at IIM campus, 10am. 
 
	Fair
  Visit J4U (jobs for you) fair, presented by The Telegraph Jobs at Rotary Sadan, 10am to 7pm.
    
	Music magic
  Enjoy an evening of foot-tapping music by Amit Kumar at GD Birla Sabhagar, 6pm.
    
	on stage
